# Task Manager Web App

## Description
A simple responsive task manager built using HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript.

## Features
- Add tasks
- Delete tasks
- Persistent storage using LocalStorage
- Responsive UI

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## How to Run
1. Download or clone the repo
2. Open index.html in a browser

## Future Improvements
- Edit tasks
- Task completion status
- Cloud sync
